Package com.android

package that contains all of our classes to do with Virtual Method Invocation, which is when we define a method and expect it to be overridden in a sub class or a class that is implementing an interface. use the Main to access all the code to deal with this topic To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
